<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="point-v">point <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /pɔɪnt/    美 /pɔɪnt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[不用于被动语态] 用 (手指等) 指；指向：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>point at / to / towards sb / sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is rude to point your finger at others.
用手指指他人是不礼貌的。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-aim">2.★ <strong>对准 (aim)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A hundred cameras were being <strong>pointed at</strong> her. 
上百个相机对准了她。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>面向；朝向：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sign post <strong>points in a</strong> wrong <strong>direction</strong>. 
路标指向错误的方向。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The needle of a compass always <strong>points to / towards</strong> the north.
罗盘的指针总指向北。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>(意思上) 指向；暗示；表明：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All the evidence <strong>pointed to / towards</strong> Tony as the thief.
所有证据都表明托尼是小偷。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="point-out">point out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>把…指出来 (给看)；指出；指明：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>pointed out to</strong> him where I used to live.
我把我过去住的地方指给他看。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>pointed out that</strong> the road was not safe in winter.
他指出这条路冬天不安全。</p></div></div>